import copy
class MaximumEntropy:
def __init__(self, max_step = 1000, threshold = 0.005):
self.max_step = max_step #
self.threshold = threshold #
# x Zw(x) Pw(y|x)
#x:
def zwx(self, x):
zx = 0
for y in self.labels: #
zx_y = 0
for xi in x: #
if (xi, y) in self.x_y:
zx_y += self.x_y[(xi, y)][1] #sum wi*fi(xi,y)
zx += math.exp(zx_y)
return zx
# x Pw(y|x)
#x:
#y:
def pyx(self, x, y):
zx = self.zwx(x)
zx_y = 0
for xi in x: #
if (xi, y) in self.x_y:
zx_y += self.x_y[(xi, y)][1] #sum wi*fi(xi,y)
return math.exp(zx_y) / zx
# xi EPF: fi(xi,y)
# Pw(y|xi)() EPF = sum P(xi)Pw(y|xi)fi(xi,y)
# xi: x
# y:
# P(xi)Pw(y|xi)=P(xi,y) P(xi) Pw(y|xi)
# P(x) Pw(y|x)
# fit P(xi,y) P(xi,y)<=>P(x,y)
#x xi
# P(x)Pw(y|x)=P(x,y)
#
def epf(self, xi, y, X):
ep = 0
for x in X:
if xi not in x:
continue #fi(x, y)=0
4
23
pyx = self.pyx(x, y) # P(y|x)
# sum P(x)P(y|x)fi(x,y) P(x)=1/Nfi(x,y)=1
ep += pyx/len(X)
return ep
#
def fit(self, X, Y):
N = len(X) #
#
#
M = len(X[0])
self.labels = set(Y) #
# (x,y)
self.x_y = {}
for i_sample in range(N):
y = Y[i_sample]
for xi in X[i_sample]:
if (xi, y) in self.x_y:
self.x_y[(xi, y)][0] += 1
else:
# (x,y) w
# EPF_HAT
self.x_y[(xi, y)] = [1, 0, 0]
# (xi,y) EPF_HAT: fi(xi,y)
# P(xi,y) EPF_HAT = sum P(xi,y)fi(xi,y)
# P(xi,y) P(xi,y)<=>P(x,y) x
# xi
for x_y in self.x_y: # (xi,y)
self.x_y[x_y][2] = self.x_y[x_y][0] / N
# IIS L(P,w)
for step in range(self.max_step):
last_x_y = copy.deepcopy(self.x_y)
# (x,y) EPF: fi(x,y)
# Pw(y|x)() EPF = sum P(x)Pw(y|x)fi(x,y)
for x_y in self.x_y: # (x,y)
ep = self.epf(*x_y, X) # i
self.x_y[x_y][1] += math.log(self.x_y[x_y][2]/ep)/M
#
stop = True
for x_y in self.x_y:
if abs(last_x_y[x_y][1]-self.x_y[x_y][1]) >=
self.threshold:
stop = False
break
if stop:
print('After {} step, maximum entropy model training

def predict(self, X):
results = []
for x in X:
zx = self.zwx(x)
result = []
for y in self.labels:
zx_y = 0
for xi in x:
if (xi, y) in self.x_y:
zx_y += self.x_y[(xi, y)][1]
result.append((y, math.exp(zx_y)/zx))
results.append(result)
return results
